There are 4 files:
1. ESPHome damper configuration file: damper.yaml
   This file provides cover, button, sensor ("my_position") and number ("stepper_control") to Home Assistant
2. Input Number to provide persistent state for damper position
3. PID2Damper automation to move the stepper to the new position 
4. A template for reversing the thermostats for heat/cool  

